=======================================================================

CHANGES:
04/07/2025 - Added "Try Demo" functionality to load question bank from GitHub repository

The following modifications were made to legacy/index.html:

1. Added a "Try Demo" button to access sample questions directly
2. Added styling for the button layout
3. Added JavaScript function loadDemoData() to fetch CSV data from GitHub
4. Refactored the game initialization process to share code between file upload and demo data load
5. Added loading state and error handling for demo data loading

These changes allow users to easily try out the application with sample questions without having to manually download and upload the question bank CSV file.

=======================================================================

Original code was created for Arnab Nandi's CSE 3241 course, enhanced with the demo functionality to improve user experience.
